This directory contains an implementation of the classic Hello World
program.

First you must install bscc and its dependencies per the main README and
INSTALL instructions.

Then, to invoke the bscc compiler:
  $ bscc -o hello.exe hello.bas

Finally, to run the program you just compiled:
  $ wine hello.exe


